    <note>Li(2) Chaozheng [975] His ancestors were Longxi jun Li(2). It is not known when they moved to Jiangning, Jurong xian. During the military disorder of the Southern Tang, they moved to Liyang xian. None of his patrilineal ancestors of the previous four generations held office. His father, Ye [3545], was Zhang(1) Gang's [252] father-in-law. Zhang Gang, WJ, 32.7a; XNYL, 152.15a, 153.2b, 2b-3a, 154.20b, 155.4a, 5a, 8a, 157.10b; SHY:ZG, 70.32b; Jingxue zhi, 5.10a. CBD, 2, 1036.</note>
